      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0659P0-08448'>
        <a name='S5LV0659P0_20040405_GCR_78'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-lucius-cary' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0659P0_20040405_GCR_78' title='Link to this speech by Mr Lucius Cary' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
