            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_543gc' title='Col. 543GC &mdash; HL Deb 05 April 2004 vol 659 c543GC' name='column_543gc' href='#column_543gc' rel='bookmark'>543GC</a>
            amendment. The amendment and the Bill do not raise the legitimacy of any testing; that comes completely outwith our considerations.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
