          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-andrew-mcintosh" title="Mr Andrew McIntosh">Lord McIntosh of Haringey</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            And it has allowed me to know!
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0659P0-08655'>
        <a name='S5LV0659P0_20040405_GCR_285'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-colin-moynihan' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0659P0_20040405_GCR_285' title='Link to this speech by Mr Colin Moynihan' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
